    "We do not know at the time of writing this paper whether the Kummer-faithfulness property holds for any e ≥ 1.",
    "Here we give a partial result on the torally Kummer-faithfulness for any e ≥ 1.",
    "Theorem 5.3.",
    "Suppose that K is a finitely generated field over Q and e is a positive integer.",
    "Then, the group G m (K(σ)) div is trivial for almost all σ ∈ G e K."
